ype = metadata"},{"type":"text","text":" if data parsing error has occurred."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Partially updating a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dataId"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each batch will be included in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}]}],"name":"Note","style":"note"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\